cat << EOF
Nobody knows military simulations like the world's premier land force, the U.S.
Army. So when the Army began making a simulation to let civilians experience
the barracks to the battlefields, it sent its talented development teams to
experience the Army as a recruit would. The developers crawled through obstacle
courses, shot weapons, parachute jumped, and visited the Army bases, all to let
you play Army in the most realistic way ever depicted in a computer game.

NOTE: 813M download, 1.9G INSTALLED

